nodes.text: Dellard Tranc was a male Genian who served as Talesan Fry's head of Security at Frys business complex.

During the Clone Wars, Tranc was visited by Obi-Wan Kenobi, who had come to negotiate with Fry about the code breakers, which he had developed. Tranc suspected that Helina Dow was the traitor until he was killed.
